title: TEXAS BOARD OF DENTAL EXAMINERS AUSTIN, TEXAS M. THOMAS

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Texas Public Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Records of complaints and inquiries against Dean Logue, Waco, Texas. Memos, emails, recordings, records of meetings of the Board, and, or, conclusions on a case against Dean Logue by Marcee Thomas, of Waco, Texas dated April l, 2022.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Bernadette Feazell

title: Barrel Babes Drag Brunch Protest in Roanoke, Texas on August 28, 2022

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

I am writing to make a Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) request for any records related to the Barrel Babes Drag Brunch protest that occurred on August 28, 2022 in Roanoke, Texas. Specifically, I am requesting any reports, documents, photographs, videos, surveillance footage, bodycam footage, audio recordings, and other materials related to the protest.

The protest involved a drag show organized by the Barrel Babes Drag Brunch and was met with opposition from armed protesters. Some of the armed protesters were reported to have been carrying assault rifles and handguns. There were also armed counter-protesters present.

The key words for this request include but are not limited to: Barrel Babes Drag Brunch, Roanoke, Texas, protest, armed protesters, armed counter-protesters, assault rifles, handguns, surveillance footage, bodycam footage, audio recordings.

Please provide any records that are responsive to this request, even if they are redacted or otherwise partially withheld. If possible, please provide an estimated date of completion for this request.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Jordan
